{"tid":1785286,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【反警文化】軍裝警等5分鐘無人招呼更遭嘲笑 美國星巴克員工遭停職","createTime":"2019-12-16T09:14:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T13:27:36.000Z","uid":28765,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"3711f3060c9474dfb5264d2befaf9abb7b5e8b8a","tid":1785286,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T09:14:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191216/large/1576439337_bffd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191216%2Flarge%2F1576439337_bffd.jpg&h=64609a98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n加州河濱縣警長比安科批評當地星巴克分店員工反警。(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n美國連鎖咖啡店星巴克（Starbucks）再捲入反警爭議。南加州河濱縣（Riverside County）兩名軍裝警員聲稱上周四在一間星巴克打算光顧時，等了五分鐘沒有員工理會更遭嘲笑，最後只好離開。<br />\n事發於加州大學河濱分校附近一間星巴克。當時店內有10至20名顧客，但沒有人排隊，兩名警員等了良久仍無人招呼，一人主動問是否有人招呼他們時，一名員工答「可能有吧」，另外幾名員工笑起來，警員黯然離開，向上司報告事件。<br />\n河濱縣警長比安科（Chad Bianco）在Twitter表示，當晚兩名警員遭到嘲笑與完全蔑視，指出星巴克員工屢次展示的反警文化必須停止。他說，兩名無咖啡喝的警員，最終在另一間星巴克分店喝到咖啡，翌日他亦請兩人到另一個品牌的咖啡店飲咖啡。<br />\n星巴克發言人博爾格斯（Reggie Borges），為員工蓄意或非蓄意不尊重執法人員致歉。星巴克表示已將當晚當更的河濱縣分店職員停職，直至調查完成。<br />\n美國星巴克今年較早時發生過兩宗涉嫌反警事件。奧克拉荷馬州一名警察上月感恩節當日到星巴克購買咖啡時，被該店員工在咖啡杯訂單上寫上「PIG」（豬）字。警員在facebook寫出經歷後，星巴克道歉，以「違反公司守則」為由把涉事員工解僱。<br />\n今年7月美國獨立日，亞利桑那州鳳凰城一間星巴克發生「請走警察」事件，事緣一名顧客見到有六名警察在店內光顧後，向店員投訴「感到不安全」，店員於是要求警員離開。星巴克後來就事件致歉。<br />\n美國有線新聞網絡／南加州《企業報》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191216/60381924\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191216%2F60381924&d=dVEf9brN%2BTtwApumOSMW7h4DU%2FdTpVEdsDcTgM8IVTs%3D&h=e328d9e6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191216%2F60381924&h=ac9f2131\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191216/60381924</a>"},{"pid":"17a4c650ab559bf38ecc9c3a1c3cef6281a78951","tid":1785286,"uid":14918,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T09:18:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今年7月美國獨立日，亞利桑那州鳳凰城一間星巴克發生「請走警察」事件，事<span style=\"color: red;\">緣一名顧客見到有六名警察在店內光顧後，向店員投訴「感到不安全」</span>，店員於是要求警員離開。星巴克後來就事件致歉。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f162e3c98caa3bc2a328d5aa6e1621a83445c5c","tid":1785286,"uid":265133,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T09:20:25.000Z","msg":"國際標準：不歡迎黑警"},{"pid":"fc360f7e917804219643d407dc0391dacfe35be0","tid":1785286,"uid":201605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T09:58:29.000Z","msg":"國際標準"},{"pid":"59feb75288c9343a586ac8e6acea7e9c6fed5b1e","tid":1785286,"uid":237425,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T10:00:04.000Z","msg":"員工冇做錯到"},{"pid":"82558761e311607ff6e24e869b2cfa5bb1089a72","tid":1785286,"uid":25468,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T10:00:05.000Z","msg":"開微博啦 , 仲 twiter ?"},{"pid":"d5a07643653764fde74734466806253c45b769ea","tid":1785286,"uid":197563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T10:01:12.000Z","msg":"The absolutely state of California"},{"pid":"e3d816c265bb3b06c51faa884b03b10da8efaf22","tid":1785286,"uid":144626,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T10:02:44.000Z","msg":"天下Starfuck一樣黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c8f76c94c121acb01015cf756b909084d19f7de","tid":1785286,"uid":265192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e3d816c265bb3b06c51faa884b03b10da8efaf22","tid":1785286,"uid":144626,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T10:02:44.000Z","msg":"天下Starfuck一樣黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gi